caption.p: The percent of seed germination inhibition in the presence of CS1 (CEO 10% + SEO 2%), CS2 (CEO 1% + SEO 0.2%), and CS3 (0.5% + SEO 0.1%). Between the mean values followed by different letters, there are statistical differences assured for p < 0.05 by t-Test, n = 3. WHEAT, ( Triticum aestivum, Antille cultivar), EGAL ( Echinochloa crus-galli), CALB ( Chenopodium album), ARET ( Amaranthus retroflexus).
